<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Article Published Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h2 {
      color: #333;
    }

    p {
      color: #666;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #999;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="container">
    <h2>New Article Published!</h2>
    <p>Hello [User Name],</p>
    <p>We're excited to inform you that [Author Name] has published a new article on Rails Titans.</p>
    <p><strong>Article Title:</strong> <%= @article&.title %></p>
    <p><strong>Summary:</strong> <%= @article&.content&.truncate(100) %></p>
    <p>Read the full article by clicking the button below:</p>
    <%= link_to 'Read Article', article_url(@article&.slug), class: 'btn'  %>
  </div>

</body>

</html>
